  "recipeDescriptionLines": [
    {
      "recipeDescriptionLine": "Methi Pulao is a vegetarian dish and a healthier option due to its rich calcium content. Fenugreek leaves has so much of other nutritional value, being enriched with minerals like  Potassium, Iron and also is a good source of dietary fiber and vitamin C. It is also known to increase milk production in lactating women."
    },
    {
      "recipeDescriptionLine": "Pulao is a dish in which rice is cooked in a seasoned broth with a combination of vegetables and spices and sometimes with chicken or egg. It is best served with Raita (yoghurt dip)."
    }
  ],
  "preface": "I found the best way to enjoy nutritional methi and thanks to my friend for this. When I had the pulao in one of the parties, i could not resist eating it. This recipe is nutritional not only because of methi but also because of different vegetables used. Enjoy this simple recipe today.",
